name: a frame of tri
description:
The triangle can also symbolize the stages of the moon- waxing, waning, full. 
Other trinities include: 
mind, body, spirit ; mother, father, child ; past, present, future ; mother, maiden, crone ; thought, feeling, emotion ; creation, preservation, destruction.
A symbol that depicts an eye, often enclosed in a triangle and surrounded by rays of light or Glory, meant to represent divine providence, whereby the eye of God watches over humanity.
